sentences: Bilal Göregen (born September 4, 1988), is a Turkish street musician and drummer.
He is blind and has become famous via his rendition of Ievan polkka, wherein a Twitter user superimposed a vibing cat on his video.
YouTube has shared his performing video on Instagram.
Born and raised in Hatay, Turkey.
Bilal Göregen has performed in O Ses Türkiye.
He earned fame by Sevdiğim kız bana abi deyince.
He had a video with the mayor of Istanbul Ekrem İmamoğlu.
He is of Kurdish origin from Bitlis.
